      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "DODGEM MOCHA (8) has been in the minor money at both career runs, the latest finishing second (22.27) at this track. Solid beginner and with a good start should have clear running out wide. Should be in this for a long way. KELSEY'S BEACH (1) last raced on February 6 when fifth (22.87) over 390m at this track in a Maiden. Rates a winning chance on best. CREEPING COLBY (2) was safely held last time out, finishing fifth at this track over 390m behind Canya Fake It (23.05) in a Maiden. Was in the money prior to that. Form from his last run is proving to be solid. Worth following up. CODE RED (7) makes debut for the Ian Hoggan kennel. Start all important and will need some luck getting across from the wide draw. Market should provide a lead to his ability.",
